Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_proper...rce_data_phase(25.10)    timing_proper...rce_data_phase(25.10)

Name
       timing_property_arrival_clocks_consider_clock_source_data_phase

Syntax
       timing_property_arrival_clocks_consider_clock_source_data_phase

       {true | false}

       Default : true

       Considers the clock source data phases.

       The   get_property   and   report_property  commands  support  the  ar-
       rival_clocks collection property on  pin  objects.  The  arrival_clocks
       property  considers  data phases, clock source data phases, and latency
       phases.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

